" [SSH]
" Useful settings when SSH-ing.
"
" You can edit a remote files as follows:
"
"     $ vim scp://remoteuser@server.tld//absolute/path/to/document
"

":mapping Toggle paste mode.
" See `:help paste` for more info on paste-mode.
set pastetoggle=<f9>

":setting The screen will not be redrawn while executing macros, registers and
" other commands that have not been typed. Also, updating the window title is
" postponed.
set lazyredraw

" vim:ft=vim
